FT  24 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Southend Property setback
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
PROFITS of Southend Property fell from Pounds 3.71m to Pounds 1.15m pre-tax
for the year to March 31. A fall in turnover from Pounds 81.1m to Pounds
